text:
E. 161st Street, east from the Macombs Dam Bridge ramp (east of Jerome Avenue). On the right is a portion of the Yankee Stadium, and straddling 161st Street is the elevated station of the IRT subway. In the right background is the Bronx County Court House and to its left is the Concourse Plaza Hotel, both at the Grand Concourse. View 2 is east from Cromwell Avenue.
P. L. Sperr
April 10, 1941
Views 1,2
